        "whats_possible": "Your deacon patrol loops failed repeatedly due to Dolt corruption, uninitialized beads databases, and environment misconfigurations — consuming entire sessions on debugging instead of patrolling. An autonomous pre-flight validation system could detect and repair these infrastructure prerequisites before the patrol even begins, turning fragile single-shot patrols into resilient loops that self-recover from corruption, restart Dolt servers, and reinitialize databases without human intervention.",
